Interface DistBusChildNetRef

All Known Implementing Classes:
DistBusChildNetRefImpl
public interface DistBusChildNetRef
extends com.interpss.dist.DistBus, IBusChildNetRef

A representation of the model object 'Dist Bus Child Net Ref'. DistBus class containing a Network object for multi-net algorithm implementation. The bus has to be a Generator bus or a mixed Load bus. The interfaceBusId defines a bus in the referenced Net object.

The following features are supported:

  • Interface Bus Id
  • Child Net Ref

See Also:
MultiNetPackage.getDistBusChildNetRef()
